I"è<p>In crypto, the <strong>Bart Formation</strong>, or just Bart, is a chart pattern where the cryptocurrency market rallies sharply, usually on a shorter timeframe like 30M, and after a period of flat (<a href="/glossary/sideways/">sideways</a>) action retraces <em>all of its previous gains</em>.</p>

